<h1>Meta Ads Complete Learning Website</h1>
<p><b>Created by: Mohan Dulam</b></p>
<p>This website explains the complete Meta (Facebook & Instagram) advertising process including setup, campaign creation, targeting, optimization and troubleshooting.</p>

<div class="section">
<h2>1. What is Meta Advertising?</h2>
<p>Meta advertising is paid promotion on Facebook, Instagram, Messenger and Audience Network to reach potential customers.</p>

<h3>Why Businesses Use Meta Ads</h3>
<ul>
<li>Lead generation</li>
<li>Website traffic</li>
<li>Online sales</li>
<li>Brand awareness</li>
<li>App installs</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>2. Meta Business Manager Setup</h2>
<ol>
<li>Create Business Manager</li>
<li>Add Facebook Page</li>
<li>Create Ad Account</li>
<li>Add payment method</li>
<li>Assign roles</li>
<li>Verify domain</li>
</ol>

<h3>Roles</h3>
<table>
<tr><th>Role</th><th>Permission</th></tr>
<tr><td>Admin</td><td>Full control</td></tr>
<tr><td>Advertiser</td><td>Create and run ads</td></tr>
<tr><td>Analyst</td><td>View reports only</td></tr>
</table>
</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>3. Meta Pixel & Tracking</h2>
<p>Meta Pixel is a tracking code installed on the website to track user behavior.</p>

<h3>Why Pixel is Important</h3>
<ul>
<li>Conversion tracking</li>
<li>Retargeting</li>
<li>Optimization</li>
</ul>

